reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This GPS screen is quite useful. It has a strong suction cup underneath that can be mounted on the car's dashboard. Its size appears clear and does not affect the field of view while driving, securing firmly in place. The installation is simple. The maps on the navigation are quite accurate so far and convenient to use, eliminating the need to constantly connect the phone to CarPlay for navigation. This makes it much more convenient to use the phone when needed. From my experience, everything has been quite satisfactory so far.
